From 057ba10e7342fe2c58479008047a9106bad80ea9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mia Gorceva <elena@mite.club>
Date: Fri, 5 Jun 2026 13:31:47 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 5/7] Make route report compact to match the value report style
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

The route report used a heavy bordered table with large DejaVu Serif fonts, while
the value report is compact (small font, thin/dashed separators). Rebuild the
route report in the same compact style: small (size 9) default font, dashed thin
cell separators, a small one-line title, date in the top-right header, and the
"Должность, ФИО, подпись" footer. The cross-tab "Диапазон ... От .. до .." columns
and the green ✓ / red ✗ Контроль column are preserved. Now both daily reports
share one visual style.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
